Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:04.40,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}These criminals are guilty \Nof murdering Bakufu officials
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:08.65,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8} as well as the leader \Nof those snooping dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:09.86,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.61,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,We've heard enough, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We already know the rest of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:18.28,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Try to commit a crime that's \Nworthy of this punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:21.07,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,What crime will you be guilty of?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The crime of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:24.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,ripping off a lord's \Ntopknot down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:25.33,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.87,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be sacrificing \Neverything for Yoshiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:30.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I already made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:34.35,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.01,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:36.76,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:39.66,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,We will all return alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:15.90,Ep Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Five Pinkies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:18.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.66,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring the old man \Nback to Suzuran together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:24.91,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Finished with your last farewells?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.64,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobume-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:29.16,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you joining us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.95,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,As a survivor of the Mimawarigumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:34.07,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,I must fulfill my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:34.67,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.67,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to cut people up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.64,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.18,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way, mobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.85,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Or else we kill the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.46,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.35,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you disrespect Her Highness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.19,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred executions wouldn't \Nbe enough to punish this crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.86,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.98,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Zip your stinkin' mouths!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.98,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Every time someone speaks, \NI cut off a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.50,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, assuming that \Nwe manage to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.37,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,we won't be able to \Nlive in Edo anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.37,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.69,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.28,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only time her \Nacting has been believable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.88,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to explain this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:15.27,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,She said to zip your stinkin' mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.64,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,That applies to me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.97,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,How many times did you speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.88,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:20.67,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.68,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like counting, \Nso I'll do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.89,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:24.75,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.99,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you talked again, \Nso one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.74,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We understand! Let them pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.97,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you talked again, \Nso one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.90,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.40,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,That went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:39.31,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No, that did not go well, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The damage to our reputation \Nis irreparable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.90,Main01,Soy,0000,0000,0000,,I was really nervous, but it was funny
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.53,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,how everyone was so surprised, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.30,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.16,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Sadisteers can shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.73,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,However, it would be dangerous to \Ncontinue this charade, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.51,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please find a place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:57.17,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me help you see this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.26,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what I was doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.51,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was the one chaining \NGrampy inside the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.18,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Grampy probably wanted \Nto leave the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:11.18,Caption Yellow,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(169,1)}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.43,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,far more than I did, but \NI never noticed a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.18,Caption Red,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Behave yourself, \NYour Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.18,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,He was always watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:14.89,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,So it's my turn to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:17.25,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means he'll \Nscold me for misbehaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.51,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Soyo-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:19.58,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:20.84,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.27,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.36,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She just knocked herself out \Nafter saying she wanted to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:33.66,Odd Jobs,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.72,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like a murder scene now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:33.66,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And why did she write Odd \NJobs as her dying message?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.00,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let anyone see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.30,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,It's faster to destroy the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.03,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:41.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I really embarrassed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,My embarrassment is faster \Nthan my mouth can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.68,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the Ikkoku-dou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.90,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,What have you bastards done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.64,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There's a whole horde coming for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:54.69,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Soyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.56,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Kill every single one of the rebels!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.82,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,No mercy for the women and children!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.01,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Women and children?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.37,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,That's some big talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.56,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, that scum \Nwould be served by scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.08,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,This nation has no respect for women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.85,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:24.63,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Show that you can stop \Nthe women you sneer at!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.95,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Show that you can defend the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.80,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,built upon the tears of those women!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.35,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've forgotten about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.31,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to remind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.06,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.68,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,These women
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.68,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,have come to topple a county.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We've got three nation \Nbreakers with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:57.16,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds tougher than \Ntaking on the shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.17,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some advice. \NCall for reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You might be the shogun's \Npersonal guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:07.68,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but you're probably too soft from \Nall the peace and quiet to take us on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, we're still at war,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:13.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,fighting for our lives every day \Nagainst those psychos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.07,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-chan, how many do we each take?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred, two hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.59,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I'm putting myself to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:44.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Stay close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:47.00,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Trust the rest of us to watch your back
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and focus on the enemies \Nin front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.59,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're standing, \Nwe're all standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Become the blade for \Ntaking down that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:59.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crush the \Nshogun's silly toy box!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to seize
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.03,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:06.61,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Form a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.32,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let these rebels \Nget any closer to our lor—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Weaker than Zazami Original!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:18.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourselves \Nthe shogun's samurai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:20.94,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,W-We can't stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:24.45,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Not from the front, the \Nright, the left, the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.74,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's no opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.80,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,The five rebels are \Nlike a giant bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.17,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:34.35,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to shoot \Ndown these crazy fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.57,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:42.14,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.76,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,W-Watch our flanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:02.75,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Second round loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.79,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Blow 'em to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:24.36,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.48,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up with the next shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:30.73,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Our comrades are inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.69,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That was mean, Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.16,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one \Ngetting this treatment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.94,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! They took the cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:49.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it to \Nthe shogun's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.17,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't see an intercom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.28,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.02,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.16,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shogun-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:02.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Come out and play!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:11.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Shogun-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:17.45,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The #1 delivery lady, the courtesan \NSuzuran, has come to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And it's too late to request a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you wash that filthy ass of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be getting any sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.33,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Life is filled with surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.94,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the first in \Nhistory to insult the Bakufu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:37.26,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and sully the Tokugawa name \Nin such a fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:42.26,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,If you intended to beg for mercy, \Nyou've only added to your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.16,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,You are the criminal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:49.60,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,I, Imai Nobume, vice-captain \Nof the Mimawarigumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.27,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,know everything you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.25,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Tokugawa Sadasada,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.78,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,you are under arrest for the \Nassassination of Bakufu officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:10:01.22,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,A surviving Hitotsubashi \Ndog is talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.54,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,judging me in a court of law?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:08.78,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,How can you judge me when \NI rule this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.54,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,When I am the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.21,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,If we cannot judge you on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.05,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,we will judge you underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:18.55,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,The woman's tears you \Nspilled in Yoshiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.90,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,The man's blood you spilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.55,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,The heavens may forgive you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.52,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,but the law in Yoshiwara, \NLady Death, will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.96,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Release that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.44,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.94,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I just asked you a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.29,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,When disaster strikes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.58,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,some choose to curse the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.50,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,When misfortune befalls you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.19,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,it is the will of the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:54.59,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,The fate the heavens have dealt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.26,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You must silently accept that fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.09,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Our blades serve as the \Nvoice of the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:01.28,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:04.10,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. That's not \Nyour ordinary cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:07.15,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,They're a group of assassins \Nwho have served
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:10.60,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the rulers of this nation from \Nthe shadows for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.84,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Men of taboo who were eliminated \Nfrom central government
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.80,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,when we entered a period of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:20.57,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,When the Oniwabanshu was disbanded,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.61,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Sadasada turned to them \Nfor his shady business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.23,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Yatagarasu for the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.50,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,The Tenshoin Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:30.25,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Oboro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:34.47,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Tenshoin and \Nthe strongest Naraku warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.75,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,That man is involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:40.19,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The one to judge is heaven. \NIn other words, the shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:43.04,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The earth-crawlers are the \Nones who are judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.01,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,That is how the world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:49.86,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,You are only allowed to \Nlook up at the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.68,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,However, you need not lament.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:54.61,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The heavens do not \Nalways bring disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:59.28,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The heavens also bring good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:03.28,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you were \Nlooking for that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.28,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gr-Grampy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:09.79,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,If you can escape alive, you will be \Nable to reunite him with Suzuran.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.30,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Though I doubt he will survive \Nlong enough to reach Yoshiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:17.29,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he does survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:23.80,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,he's lost the pinky he swore on \Nand the arm he used to hold her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:27.09,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,He should just end his miserable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:31.82,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,So much for loyalty when he's \Nbetrayed me not once, but twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:34.67,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The heavens are punishing \Nhim as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:39.98,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's literally an \Nearth-crawling worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The pinky he swore on is still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He's got five pinkies right \Nhere that are gonna drag you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.86,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,from heaven to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.41,Main01,Grampy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.87,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You've endured so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.92,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You've been through so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:40.43,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that you had to wait so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:42.87,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.92,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,The moon you have longed for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:46.91,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,has risen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.68,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,In the land where you once made a vow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:53.93,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,there is a light that will \Nshine through any darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.95,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,This moon will never fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.43,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi, Kagura, please guide him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.44,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring up the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.45,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm allowed to cut down \Nwhoever I want now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.69,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:11.20,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,In the morning, this will have \Nbeen nothing more than a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:19.21,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,You're buying time for \Nan old man to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.20,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you can escape
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.17,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,from my grasp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:31.22,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is it gonna be the sun or the \Nmoon that sits up in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:33.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, heavenly errand boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.73,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.50,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Gintoki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.27,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.24,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to die, I'll \Ncut you up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.88,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,You were hit in a pressure point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.77,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,By a poisoned needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.00,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,It'll paralyze you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.28,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,and kill you if the poison isn't removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.53,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:23.62,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to see someone \Nlast so long against you, Oboro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.55,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's happened once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:34.58,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,There was a demon who chose \Nto oppose the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:44.08,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You still have that same \Nlook in your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.06,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,White Yaksha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yo—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.15,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Gintoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:54.66,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Do you know him, Oboro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:58.66,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord, he is an orphan \Nof the Kansei purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.16,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Kansei purge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.51,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from Yoshiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.67,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Then you wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.95,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The Joi war...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:11.78,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,When the nation was opened \Nup, the ignorant samurai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:17.18,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,accused the Bakufu of selling \Nthe country and revolted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:22.93,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,As our relationship with the Amanto \Nsoured, we put down the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:27.19,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since, this nation has \Nbeen in a state of civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:31.97,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,As the war dragged on, the Amanto \Nbegan intervening in domestic affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:36.03,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,under the pretense \Nof cleansing the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:41.20,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Ironic that the Joi revolt led \Nto increased Amanto influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:45.20,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,And then the Tendoshu instructed \Nthe Bakufu to initiate
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:49.21,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the deadliest cleansing of the \Ncentury, the Kansei purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:53.99,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Every last Joi rebel, from \Nthe minor agitators to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:57.68,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the public officials, was \Ntargeted as part of the purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:03.22,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The brutal crackdown led to a \Nsharp decline in Joi activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:08.75,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Oboro and his brethren were \Ninstrumental in that process.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:12.05,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,They were led by his predecessor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:17.24,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was every bit as \Nskilled in the martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:21.43,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord, that wasn't the \Nend of the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:26.25,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,While many samurai threw away their \Nswords after losing their leaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:31.25,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,some were plotting to rescue \None of those captive leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:36.26,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,They were these men, the ones \Nknown as the last samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.61,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,They were the students of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.26,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the evil criminal who dared \Nto oppose the heavens,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.90,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida Shoyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:50.21,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,His students took up their swords \Nto rescue their teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.77,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gintoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:55.11,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You lost your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:59.03,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recall that name, my Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:02.66,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida Shoyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:07.16,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Was there such a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.27,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I remember the corpses of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:11.67,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,every worm I stomped on my way to power?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.79,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,If he happened to be a major \Ncriminal, I might remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.67,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,What was his crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:21.68,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I can't recall either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:25.41,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,I do remember that he \Ntaught sword and pen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.68,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to some children in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.28,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,That was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:33.46,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,However, my Lord, we \Nwere told to crush such gatherings
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:37.69,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,as they might foment rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:42.19,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I see. And I was correct to order that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:43.96,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida Shoyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:47.70,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,His crime was creating\N dissenters like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.25,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Gintoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:03.85,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the demon who battled the \Nheavens and fell to the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.14,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,still wandering around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:14.01,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the demon who lost everything \Nto the heavens still howling at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:18.32,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You, all of you, should \Nhave learned your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:22.65,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You can shout, you can scream,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.07,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,but your voices will \Nnever reach the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.26,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,And neither will your sobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:33.74,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Gintoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.92,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Will you make the same mistake \Nagain, White Yaksha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:43.93,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You can sit there and watch \Nuntil you bleed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:49.64,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,As everything you tried to \Nprotect is destroyed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.42,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Shoyo is also watching
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:55.98,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,as the student he sacrificed \Nhis life to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.44,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,falls apart without protecting a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:08.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:12.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.95,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Gintoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:28.55,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:30.55,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.06,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.36,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:04.30,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here \Nso late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:07.80,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, could you please \Nshow me your license?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:09.72,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:12.27,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,This is the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.93,Tsuzuku,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:48.31,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:49.61,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:52.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding. I'm getting \Ngoosebumps already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:54.76,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, when we go to the \Ntheater this summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:56.91,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,How many Pokemon will we get?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:23:59.87,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're excited about that one?!
